{"tid":2011622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反駁CCTVB曾女士個POST】 帶比我地一個逆向思維, 就是不斷向藍絲散播無力感！令佢地變中立撚！","createTime":"2020-05-11T06:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T10:38:10.000Z","uid":167548,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f634b119a934b4343ea7a01a4fa2a1a4792305","tid":2011622,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:28:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">「警察一個月收十幾萬, 你地咁支持佢地, 有冇分到錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n「警察一次毒品案偷左25公斤冰毒, 一年落來咪有幾百公斤, 咁咪好和味？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n「支持警察就可以唔守法咩, 你地咪一樣是蟻民賤民, 犯法就是犯法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n「中國搞左一單全球肺炎出嚟, 全世界廠家搬離中國, 講咩大灣區啊, 上面都沒工開, 大陸人遲啲落嚟搶我地飯碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n「我個藍絲朋友話上年班黃絲搞搞震, 都搵到下食, 有工開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇下個垃圾政府搞到我手停口停四個幾月, 我今次射落海都唔投民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我班藍絲朋友都想睇下班黃絲可以搞成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黃絲定阿爺揸旗關我地咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n大家記唔記得反送中之前中共港共propaganda, 不斷渲染黃營是少數派, 不斷話你地做咩都無用, 大量黃營犬儒助功, 好成功洗左香港人腦。今次我地應該食住個勢去做「大外宣」反攻, 應該<strong>不斷向藍絲散播無力感！令佢地變中立撚！</span></strong><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>利申上面有好多非「黃絲正確字眼」, 但大外宣就要咁樣, 扮中立, 扮自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0ba229b2f4d0cf55c3fb8b83af272fce3180c594","tid":2011622,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"問題係冇人做呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc68e53983a26611fb98884f214d19aee055eda","tid":2011622,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:31:10.000Z","msg":"仔細研究"},{"pid":"900463bbc07234aa80f7bc59e669cec4021b6a16","tid":2011622,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:31:54.000Z","msg":"藍絲會話肺炎係美國搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fb2183cde997a4feabd7ffa8ee9ea4edcb6e75","tid":2011622,"uid":167548,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:32:22.000Z","msg":"求幫手推+Share, 希望大家有一個新思維, 擴闊戰線。唔洗Connect藍營, 但要令地無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;「冷嘲熱諷」唔一定打自己人, 可以是消滅敵人的支持者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n其實反送中初期做過下整長輩圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;其實幾有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;同樣「冷嘲熱諷」可以令淺黃變中立, 一樣可以淺藍變中立。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c76e9f092b36b47a0bd45edfaa40dda83ca4bd9","tid":2011622,"uid":258598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c7a3ff747e9aedbd395766d5b4a33e2cbdfe55f","tid":2011622,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0ba229b2f4d0cf55c3fb8b83af272fce3180c594","tid":2011622,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"問題係冇人做呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:33:37.000Z","msg":"我相信點都有智障藍絲朋友, 工作上同事一樣「冷嘲熱諷」一番<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3385d4eb26a7f67b4e7144274452c2d75a0fd7f","tid":2011622,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e875ea6d5446a4fc40c69c045241dda2992eab6e","tid":2011622,"uid":8874